token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">v-for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item in objects<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">:for</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">:id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">:value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">v-model</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>&#123;&#123;item&#125;&#125;\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>您选择的目标/爱好有：&#123;&#123;target&#125;&#125;<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> example <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Vue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    el<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#app\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    data<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n        target<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        objects<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'前端开发'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'移动开发'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'H5开发'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'JavaScript'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>运行效果如下：</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210405073603482.gif#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"v-model修饰符\"><a href=\"#v-model修饰符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"v-model修饰符\"></a>v-model修饰符</h2><h3 id=\"lazy修饰符\"><a href=\"#lazy修饰符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"lazy修饰符\"></a>lazy修饰符</h3><p>默认情况下，v-model默认是在input事件中同步输入框的数据的。</p>\n<p>也就是说，一旦有数据发生改变，对应的data中的数据就会自动发生改变。</p>\n<p><strong>lazy修饰符</strong>可以让数据在失去焦点或者回车时才会更新</p>\n<h3 id=\"number修饰符\"><a href=\"#number修饰符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"number修饰符\"></a>number修饰符</h3><p>默认情况下，在输入框中无论我们输入的是字母还是数字，都会被当做字符串类型进行处理。</p>\n<p>但是如果我们希望处理的是数字类型，那么最好直接将内容当做数字处理。</p>\n<p>number修饰符可以让在输入框中输入的内容自动转成数字类型</p>\n<h3 id=\"trim修饰符\"><a href=\"#trim修饰符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"trim修饰符\"></a>trim修饰符</h3><p>如果输入的内容首尾有很多空格，通常我们希望将其去除</p>\n<p>trim修饰符可以过滤内容左右两边的空格</p>\n","feature":null,"text":"v-model原理v-model 其实是一个语法糖，它的背后本质上是包含两个操作： v-bind绑定一个value属性 v-on指令给当前元素绑定input事件 参考代码 &lt;input type=\"text\" v-model=\"message\"> &lt;!-- 等同于下面...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.8k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":12,"path":"api/categories/前端.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":12,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#v-model%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">v-model原理</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#v-model%E4%B8%8Eradio\"><span class=\"toc-text\">v-model与radio</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#v-model%E4%B8%8Echeckbox\"><span class=\"toc-text\">v-model与checkbox</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#v-model%E4%B8%8Eselect\"><span class=\"toc-text\">v-model与